A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Hunting – Nonlead Ammunition, Fox Chasing, and Deer Management
3 FOR the purpose of altering the definition of “hunt” to include the sport of fox chasing;
4 establishing the Deer Management Assistance Program in the Department of
5 Natural Resources; requiring the Department of Budget and Management, on or
6 before a certain date, to increase the number of full–time employees in the
7 Department of Natural Resources to administer the Program; requiring the
8 Department of Natural Resources to require, through a certain phasing–out process,
9 the use of nonlead ammunition for the hunting of all game species on or before a
10 certain date; establishing a certain exemption and a certain requirement for any
11 person who participates in unarmed fox chasing; and generally relating to hunting.
